"Welcome, I wish to join your group, as well as my lovely wife Inzola deos,
I am Deemos, I am considered deadly to everyone who knows me!" Deemos said.
Inzola walked forward and winked.

"You are the Predacons, right? Take us to your leader!" Inzola said to
Perndabot. Deemos looked at BrightBlade. This one was familiar to him, even
though he had never seen her. Bah, must have been someone Gangon knew! He
thought...
